✅ 卡片模板设置

样式（CSS）：

```css .card { font-family: "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: #fefefe; color: #333; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; }

h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a; }

.cloze { font-weight: bold; color: #007acc; background-color: #e6f2fb; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 4px; }

.nightMode .cloze { color: #4da8ff; background-color: #223344; }

h2 { font-size: 22px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #222; }

hr { margin: 24px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }

.note { font-size: 16px; color: #999; margin-top: 12px; } ```

